                <h1>Casting call for “volunteer” Super Bowl halftime performers enrages dance community</h1>
                <h2 class="deck">Dancer and activist Taja Riley posted what appear to be screenshots of the call — which indicates participants will be required to rehearse for 72 unpaid hours — on Instagram Wednesday.</h2>

            </div>

          </div>

          
          <div class="credits gutter_left triple_gutter_right">
              <div class="author">
    <span>
      By <span class="credit_name"><a href="/contributor/raphael-helfand">Raphael Helfand</a></span>
  </div>


<div class="posted">
  <div>
    January 25, 2022
  </div>
</div>

          </div>

